      <title>保守党多年危机后，市场渴望斯塔默带来稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/markets-crave-stability-from-starmer-after-years-of-tory-crises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在英国政坛历史性的选举之夜之后，伦敦金融城的投资者不断用一个词来表达他们对英国市场下一时代的希望：稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/markets-crave-stability-from-starmer-after-years-of-tory-crises</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 10:05:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克为选举失败道歉，表示将辞去保守党领袖职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-05/sunak-apologizes-says-he-s-resigning-as-tory-leader-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将卸任的英国首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 在保守党在英国大选中遭遇历史性失败后在唐宁街 10 号外发表讲话。苏纳克表示：“我将辞去党魁一职，但不是立即，而是在正式安排好继任者后。” (来源：彭博社)]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-05/sunak-apologizes-says-he-s-resigning-as-tory-leader-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 10:05:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪的主要联盟盟友寻求超过 120 亿美元的援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/modi-s-top-coalition-ally-seeks-more-than-12-billion-handout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪联合政府的一位重要盟友要求为其管辖的印度南部邦提供超过 1 万亿卢比（120 亿美元）的财政支持，这给联邦预算增添了压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/modi-s-top-coalition-ally-seeks-more-than-12-billion-handout</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 09:46:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Biocon Biologics 考虑发行高达 5.4 亿美元的卢比债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/biocon-biologics-mulls-raising-up-to-540-million-in-rupee-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Biocon Biologics Ltd. 正考虑在几个月内从印度本币债券市场筹集 400 亿卢比至 450 亿卢比（5.4 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/biocon-biologics-mulls-raising-up-to-540-million-in-rupee-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 09:43:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>星展银行因违反反洗钱规定遭香港罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/dbs-fined-by-hong-kong-for-violating-anti-money-laundering-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[星展集团控股有限公司因未遵守反洗钱和反恐怖主义融资法规，被香港监管机构罚款 1000 万港元（128 万美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/dbs-fined-by-hong-kong-for-violating-anti-money-laundering-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 09:20:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞驳斥民意调查称极右翼未能在法国占据多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/le-pen-rejects-polls-showing-far-right-short-of-french-majority</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞否认了有关她所在的极右翼国民联盟党在法国立法选举中无法获得绝对多数的预测，并警告说，如果她得不到执政授权，她将陷入“泥潭”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/le-pen-rejects-polls-showing-far-right-short-of-french-majority</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 07:20:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管股市创下历史新高，比特币仍跌至 2 月以来的最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/bitcoin-btc-drops-for-fourth-day-even-as-global-stocks-hit-records</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心政府、交易所破产的债权人和陷入困境的加密矿工可能会抛售比特币，比特币连续第四个交易日下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/bitcoin-btc-drops-for-fourth-day-even-as-global-stocks-hit-records</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 01:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业数据或为宽松政策提供线索，黄金有望周度上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/gold-pushes-higher-as-investors-expect-fed-will-start-to-ease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预期美联储将在年底前降息，黄金价格连续两周上涨，交易员们正在关注美国非农就业数据，以寻找下一批经济前景的线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/gold-pushes-higher-as-investors-expect-fed-will-start-to-ease</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 00:04:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市飙升、美国库存下降，油价接近两个月高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价接近两个月高点，全球股市创下历史新高，美国库存减少，增强了人们对夏季反弹的乐观情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 23:37:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业数据公布前全球股市创历史新高：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/asian-equities-to-tread-water-before-us-jobs-data-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在关键的美国就业数据公布之前，全球股市创下历史新高，预计就业数据将显示出招聘有所放缓。随着工党在英国大选中获胜，英镑创下了四年来最长的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/asian-equities-to-tread-water-before-us-jobs-data-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 22:19:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
